reviews.review_text:
My ears like this Aud best~ I streamed this one today - 37 years after it was performed - and I felt that this Joe D'Amico Aud pull sounded best overall.  I compared it closely with two other Aud sources - the Oade #23442 and the McCue/Ford #34778 - and while both are very good, this one seemed to have a brightness that the other two lacked.
God Bless the Grateful Dead~
